<H1>Session Cookies</H1>
<P>A session cookie may be used to allow our server to maintain your connection and privileges from one web page to the next. You can set your browser to notify you when you receive a cookie, giving you the chance to decide whether to accept it or not. Session cookies expire when you shut down your browser. 
<H1>Server Logs</H1>
<P>Our server automatically logs information about visits to our website in the normal course of establishing and maintaining web connections. Server logs record statistical information such as IP addresses, types of operating systems, and pages requested. These statistics are used to administer our website. Server logs are kept only as long as necessary for security purposes, and are purged on a regular basis.
